Package io.github.protonmc.proton_checkstyle_checks

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    FromModuleCheck
    A check that verifies that all Mixin methods have a configurable annotation (by default FromModule).
    ModuleSuffixCheck
    A check that forces all subclasses of a configurable superclass to have a certain configurable suffix at the end of their name.
